//
// § PRIME-DIRECTIVE  ‼ structurally-encoded
//
//   t∞: lens default-deny  ←  Unconsented refuses project()
//   t∞: revoke permanent   ←  silent re-enable = bug
//   t∞: bounds enforced    ←  AxisOutOfRange on any out-of-range index
//   t∞: overflow refused   ←  checked_add/sub instead of wrap
